rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0001
rows.name: Those are your orders. Have I made myself clear?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0002
rows.name: Quite.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0003
rows.name: You seem displeased, Ga Jiarg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0004
rows.name:
Perhaps the great hero of Wroth
does not enjoy taking orders from the Ganglion? [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0005
rows.name: Perhaps he feels it...beneath him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0006
rows.name: It appears nothing is beneath me of late.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Heh. I still hear the anger in your voice,
the way you spit out the words.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0008
rows.name: Accept your fate...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0008_2
rows.name:
Then you might find me a more...
accommodating master, Prince Jiarg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Oh, but how rude of me...
Should I have said "former prince"?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0010
rows.name: I never cared much for titles, Councilor Luxaar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0011
rows.name: It's "Grandmaster," damn you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0012
rows.name:
The entire Ganglion organization is at my commandâ€”
as are you and your people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0013
rows.name: I will not remind you again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0014
rows.name:
Oh, but how rude of me.
My sincere apologies, Grandcouncilor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0015
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0016
rows.name:
Have you also forgotten the price the Wrothian people
will pay if you fail me? I promise you, it will not be pretty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0017
rows.name:
What will happen if the humans beat you to the prize, hmm?
...Need I remind you of that as well?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0018
rows.name: No, you need not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0019
rows.name:
Then mind your tongue, former prince,
unless your pride can feed and clothe your people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs06130100_MSG0020
rows.name:
Filthy cur. Yet I will suffer him gladly...
if he can help lead me to you, oh Great One.[ST:wait ]
